Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DIALOGUE
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.26,0:00:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So boss, this is what I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:04.48,0:00:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's so cold outside, but my heart is filled with warmth."
Dialogue: 3,0:00:09.10,0:00:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's all thanks to you."
Dialogue: 3,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.65,0:00:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll quietly take her hand, pull her to my chest, and...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.13,0:00:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boss, you listening?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Christmas date fantasy, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who's gonna go on a date with you?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over if you say that!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.67,0:00:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, how're things going between you and Tanamachi?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.26,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?  You went crazy looking for her when she was absent the other day.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san told me all about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how'd that go?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:47.02,0:00:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:51.94,0:00:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you should just go ask him out.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big events like these don't come everyday.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right around the corner.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.86,0:02:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:55.76,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a paper cut.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have a bandage on you?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get me a bandage...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, please!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get me one!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.35,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, I'll die if you don't hurry!  Ow...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you some from the infirmary.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, boss!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something interesting happen?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.24,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  It's almost Christmas, isn't it?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.62,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tanaka-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then.  Time to sew this...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:43.88,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, hi!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the infirmary!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were Keiko...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here instead?!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time job, I guess...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a job for you, then.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.04,0:04:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A job?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umehara got a paper cut on his finger, so I need some bandages.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  Bandages, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.  Will one do?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you dressed like that in school?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.20,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Keiko just told me the hem of my skirt was a bit loose,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's fixing it right now.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have PE today, so I didn't bring in my jersey.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.09,0:04:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, I found my clean work uniform in my bag.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go since Umehara's waiting.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  It's... well...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, do you have any plans for Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying this late?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when we're having our date, of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you weren't gonna ask me, so I just made the date myself.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not... really...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scored a date with Kaoru on Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.88,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing her in that uniform at the\Ninfirmary was pretty refreshing, though.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:27.51,0:05:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you were thinking about something weird, weren't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see Keiko, tell her to bring my uniform back to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.11,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas dinners are expensive no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's expensive to do anything on Christmas.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.26,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything costs about 20 percent more.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 percent more?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.25,0:06:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People going on Christmas dates have a lot to worry about.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.78,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well Nii-nii, it doesn't really concern you anyway.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year, I'll...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nii-nii?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.88,0:06:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.87,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,This year... This year...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the meat buns we just ate...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda want to just go and buy something new, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve... and my first date!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outfit is important, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I wear my fancy underwear?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:45.35,0:06:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided to go there with Junichi.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations seem to be coming along nicely.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  We ran into some problems, but we're doing fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With more people participating in the garage sale,
Dialogue: 3,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Founder's Festival gets bigger and bigger by the year.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Festival Committee President.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, it's still too early to say that.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  For me?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:15.23,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since you can't make it to our party later.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's one from me.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything for you, though...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to go to the Christmas party too...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's throw another one tomorrow!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.23,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Christmas Eve, but it's still Christmas!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I agree!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Swim Club made some Oden.  Do you want some?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:45.12,0:07:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared the daikon radishes.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been cooking since yesterday, so it'll be tasty!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to distribute leaflets for the tea party?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Rihocchi.  You're in charge of promoting it!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you to bring us more guests.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rihocchi.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear this while you're at it.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely gather more attention this way.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:09.41,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'll try...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru sure is late.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how she is.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.51,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected her to be 10 or 20 minutes late, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was naïve.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to have to wait for more than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is she not coming?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:42.33,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be stood up again like I was two years ago?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaoru wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always shows up, no matter how late.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!  Really late!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:11.04,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth were you doing?!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I went a little overboard with some stuff.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be trying harder to get here on time instead.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why I apologized.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologizing doesn't make it okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be mad.  Cheer up.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.00,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just worried.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't going to show up.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd do something you don't like.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's our all-important first date.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, smile!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's kinda gross.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't make me do it!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:58.79,0:10:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back to your normal self again.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to butt in.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get going.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where to?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.45,0:10:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... that Port Tower you told me about?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:23.45,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty tall when you look at it up close!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we go up the tower?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go up this thing?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.10,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a park here...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can go for a walk.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you pervert.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.06,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't walking along the shore like this bring back memories?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.22,0:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in middle school, didn't we use to walk home like this after hanging out?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.93,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umehara-kun chased you, and you panicked and dove straight into the girl's bathroom.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:02.55,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also got a nosebleed from falling asleep\Nduring class and smashing your head on the desk.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you bring up better memories at a time like this?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the time you tried to prank me, but got your nuts kicked instead!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the same vein, you're always doing crazy things.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skirt flipped up all the time, and everyone could see your underwear.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking too, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd jump on the back of my bike and ask me to give you a ride....
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, didn't we fall really hard once?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you were thrashing around.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.  Let's get going.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.53,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the time when the night scenery is best.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far, so of course we're going up there.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get in.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long, Hibiki-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for the Miss Santa contest?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't that end already?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It did...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:30.82,0:12:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl who won didn't accept\Nher victory because I didn't participate,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.05,0:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so now we're facing off one-on-one.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, come with me.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that outfit a little small?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.20,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda against the rules, in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're afraid of heights?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come here!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.  Here, here.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0\fscx140} {\r}afraid of heights!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just don't like it because it's cold by the window.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me cute!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-As long as I don't look down, I can handle this...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, not bad.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is nothing.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, they'll see your panties from below...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're wearing pants.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they can't.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I mind.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing my fancy under{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out, out, out!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really {\i1}are{\i0\fscx140} {\r}afraid of heights!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.19,0:14:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel better if we hold hands like this?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stay like this for a while.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's snowing!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll be a white Christmas...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really wonderful.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.94,0:14:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kinda weird to watch falling snow from above?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we witnessed something special.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rare coincidence.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm being sucked in.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.01,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:48.28,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the city seem small when\Nyou look down from a place this high up?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was born and raised here...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:59.33,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.59,0:15:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I fell in love here.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:08.86,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's something I want to tell you today.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buddies, pals, inseparable...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many ways to describe our relationship.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want any distance between us anymore.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.33,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally realized my own feelings.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:28.69,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until recently, I was satisfied with simply pulling you around.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:33.28,0:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that all ended a while ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:37.14,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was being pulled by you.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:43.12,0:15:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've built up so many memories over time,\Nand that's what led me to realize my feelings.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.02,0:15:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say 100 bad things about you.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say 101 good things about you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi, I...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so uncool.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made you say something you normally wouldn't.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you idiot.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.70,0:16:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're fine with someone like me, I'll be with you forever.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things haven't been clear between us,
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I have the confidence to say this.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you forever, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I be with you?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing just one line.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you too, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Thanks for having me over today.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed the last bus home.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna come over?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.50,0:17:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and dad left for the hot springs today, so Miya's the only one home.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'd only be a bother.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just spend the night at a family restaurant or a convenience store.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.98,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't possibly let you do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:00.28,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll come over.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:15.91,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:28.69,0:18:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  It just occurred to me that we've known each other for a while now,
Dialogue: 3,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the first time I've ever been to your room.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised at how tidy it is.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of room were you expecting?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something more{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, don't tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.  Wait...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:52.81,0:18:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, you're not spending the night at Ume-chan's place this year?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard someone else just now.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell even if you hide it.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.70,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching porn because you're feeling so lonely for being alone at Christmas.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the volume down, okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said you're wrong!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.78,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm safe, but why do I feel like I lost?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice and understanding sister.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was this what she meant by porn?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.00,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.43,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why are there stars on the walls of your closet?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my special place.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This closet?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be honest.  That's weird.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I lick your wound?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was also a joke.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's sleep together.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a joke too?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna sleep on the floor.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really gonna sleep together?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just be sleeping next to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home before Miya-chan wakes up in the morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just sleep in the closet.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with sleeping together?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's kinda...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something better than stars.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:24.61,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.74,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My heart's beating way too fast!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to calm down...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya's the one sleeping behind me.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:44.06,0:20:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miya, who has terrible sleeping habits and drools in her sleep!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it... believe it!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Kaoru sleeping already?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:00.17,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can at least see her sleeping face, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:15.88,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were awake?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  What were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What do you mean?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:30.96,0:21:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru, I couldn't breathe...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.64,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaoru.  You're not actually sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.19,0:22:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our relationship has taken a step forward,
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.27,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's even more fun waiting for us in the future, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.93,0:23:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode preview.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up in the next episode, Nakata-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.01,0:23:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.82,0:23:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakata Sae, and I'm 15 years old.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:59.08,0:24:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice... t-to meet you.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:01.43,0:24:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakata-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:02.58,0:24:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem really nervous already.  Are you all right?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:05.15,0:24:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'll try harder.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:07.39,0:24:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:09.59,0:24:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Underclassman".
Dialogue: 3,0:24:11.73,0:24:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having met one summer, the boy\Nand girl are swept into the wheel of love.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wheel of... love?
